<lb ed="I" n="0255a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0255a0101">齊馮翊王　高潤之碑</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0255b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">本文</cb:mulu><head>本文</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0255b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0255b0101"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">齊</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">馮</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">翊</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">金</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">像</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">碑</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0255b02" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">蓋</unclear>□功<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">惟</unclear>遐□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">通</unclear>言<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">在</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">非</unclear>在。自道成□□。□闡鷲山。大則照神光於大千。微則摠百億於微芥。乘權授手。津被塵沙。有感斯
<lb ed="I" n="0255b03" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">應</unclear>。□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">金</unclear>□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">長</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">門</unclear>。　□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>西林。□教□於東夏。真言<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">邇</unclear>廣。靈□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">弗</unclear>興。不有覺人。孰弘斯道。至若拔山移海之力。復夏興周
<lb ed="I" n="0255b04" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□。□□□□□□□□□上之侶。或負氣□門。延葉累世。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">或</unclear>神化澹泊。百祀千齡。莫不委骨高於山岳。屑淚多於河海。共轉輪迴之苦。同
<lb ed="I" n="0255b05" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歸</unclear>□□□□。□□月□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">寧</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">彼</unclear>岸。平等寺<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">者</unclear>。□□平□□□所<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">立</unclear>。永平中造定光銅像一區。高二丈八尺。永熙年金塗訖功。像在寺外。未得
<lb ed="I" n="0255b06" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">移</unclear>□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">皇</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">綱</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">紊</unclear>□□大<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">姦</unclear>□□□□□□□大殿正屋。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">京</unclear>邑為豺狼之窟。皇居成戰鬥之場。四海分崩。八宏淪<note n="0255001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31128"/>＝喪【史】</note><note n="0255001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31128"/>【佛拓】，喪【史】</note><app n="0255001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31128"/></rdg></app>。人物將盡。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">盛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">業</unclear>□□。　□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">祖</unclear>神□皇<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>。□□□□□□□□先天奉時<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">觀</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">作</unclear>。於是虎視豹<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">變</unclear>。鷹揚鵲起。補西北之虧天。紐東南之<note n="0255002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡙇＝缺【史】</note><note n="0255002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡙇【佛拓】，缺【史】</note><app n="0255002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">缺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡙇</rdg></app>地。大拯蒼生。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b08" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">康</unclear>滋<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">頹</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">自</unclear>崤函西割。□□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>城□烽□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">畿</unclear>甸機<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">衝</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淪</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">褫</unclear>。便使<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">七</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">政</unclear>。難齊衣冠。道<app type="star" corresp="#0255002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">缺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡙇</rdg></app>將令。五禮僭制。謀遷協於卿士。卜從
<lb ed="I" n="0255b09" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear>決<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">蓍</unclear>龜。上下剋從。大同□□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>□皇輿□□□□詔移。鞏洛遂空。城<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">寺</unclear>云毀。銅駝之術。無復連<note n="0255003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䮽＝鑣【史】</note><note n="0255003" resp="ihp" type="mod">䮽【佛拓】，鑣【史】</note><app n="0255003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鑣</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䮽</rdg></app>。金馬之門。寧聞待詔。荒涼宮室。禾黍生
<lb ed="I" n="0255b10" type="honorific"/>悲。寂<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">漠</unclear>池臺。丘墟流歎。　□祖以王<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">業</unclear>草<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">創</unclear>。逋寇<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">猶</unclear>□。志去關<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">泥</unclear>。觀兵故洛。見像瓌奇。神徵屢感。莊嚴具足。相好如真。若出崛山。猶居祇樹。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b11" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">時</unclear>流<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">運</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">謝</unclear>。隱晦<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">多</unclear>紀。遂使<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>月<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淨</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">青</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">蓮</unclear>未<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遷</unclear>福地。達人弘道。觸<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">物</unclear>兼<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">懷</unclear>。發菩提覺心。希無上正果。躬親致禮。遷像入寺。登給羽林。長
<lb ed="I" n="0255b12" type="honorific"/>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">守</unclear>□。武定末。　世宗文<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">襄</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">皇</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>。□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幸</unclear>河<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">洛</unclear>。歷攬周京。<note n="0255004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">覩＝睹【史】</note><note n="0255004" resp="ihp" type="mod">覩【佛拓】，睹【史】</note><app n="0255004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">睹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">覩</rdg></app>佛儀相。世未嘗有。身色光明。實所希妙。崇申禮敬。廣施軍資。增給兵力。因
<lb ed="I" n="0255b13" type="honorific"/>□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">而</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">年</unclear>代<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">驟</unclear>改。□□非固。□石<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">尚</unclear>□。□廬易毀。簷甍傾<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">褫</unclear>。結構崩頹。駁蘚上於雕梁。<note n="0255005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31129"/>＝青【史】</note><note n="0255005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31129"/>【佛拓】，青【史】</note><app n="0255005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">青</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31129"/></rdg></app>苔衣於藻<note n="0255006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">丼＝井【史】</note><note n="0255006" resp="ihp" type="mod">丼【佛拓】，井【史】</note><app n="0255006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">井</lem><rdg wit="【原】">丼</rdg></app>。遊麤積座。等形住於慧禪。草莽生
<lb ed="I" n="0255b14" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">懷</unclear>。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">神</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">留</unclear>於智<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">崇</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear>□□□。□□□枯。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淨</unclear>土之內。蓊為茂草。太宰河陽道大行臺錄尚書事馮翊王高潤。即　神武皇帝之稚子。　文襄。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b15" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">景</unclear>烈。　<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孝</unclear>昭。　武成四<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">皇</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">弟</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">今</unclear>　<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">懿</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">叔</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">稟</unclear>精瑤室。分萼鄧林。叡氣所膺。誕茲英哲。可謂崑山之上美玉挺生。瀛海之中明珠間出。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b16" type="honorific"/>□□迥□□□自□□□數仞。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">崖</unclear>岸平□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">好</unclear>士匪梁燕之儔。富學豈簡平之背。既能調通四氣。宣導三光。鼎餗由其致和。禮教因之敬洽。飛
<lb ed="I" n="0255b17" type="honorific"/>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">真</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">問</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">忠</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樹</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聲</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">揮</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">旄</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">方</unclear>□□□□□□□□□土<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">宇</unclear>。受脤而靜關河。德若膏蘇。恩同雲雨。出軍命將。必稟策以折衝。掠地屠城。會諮謀於
<lb ed="I" n="0255b18" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帷</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幄</unclear>。王既<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">通</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">明</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">二</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">洞</unclear>□三□。知佛□□□□□□□之究竟。護浮<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">囊</unclear>於苦海。檥寶棹於金河。自推轂專征。□戎奉律。治兵餘暇。降志玄道。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b19" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鳴</unclear>鑾展禮。蹔駐騑服。俄見繡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雉</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">飛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>梁□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">文</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">貍</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">起</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>□中。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歎</unclear>淨宮之彫毀。嗟伽藍之落構。永言舊事。思用脩復。割捨侔於<note n="0255007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢁙＝布【史】</note><note n="0255007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢁙【佛拓】，布【史】</note><app n="0255007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">布</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢁙</rdg></app>金。窮材磬於文
<lb ed="I" n="0255b20" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梓</unclear>。匠人單五<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">都</unclear>之妙。畫<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">繪</unclear>極□土之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">奇</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">崢</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">嶸</unclear>□□。□□□□。□<note n="0255008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虬＝虯【史】</note><note n="0255008" resp="ihp" type="mod">虬【佛拓】，虯【史】</note><app n="0255008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虬</rdg></app>糾於鯨棟。扶<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鳳</unclear>竦於紅梁。類玄圃之銀樓。等蓬萊之玉闕。天衣容<note n="0255009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧚞＝裔【史】</note><note n="0255009" resp="ihp" type="mod">𧚞【佛拓】，裔【史】</note><app n="0255009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">裔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧚞</rdg></app>。颺三
<lb ed="I" n="0255b21" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">銖</unclear>之重。像色□□。□十力<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□。□□□□□□□□□□□□始可言矣。寺則<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">背</unclear>彼崇邙。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">面</unclear>茲清洛。右依城雉。左帶洪陂。嵩岳<note n="0255010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢹬＝擁【史】</note><note n="0255010" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢹬【佛拓】，擁【史】</note><app n="0255010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">擁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢹬</rdg></app>其<note n="0255011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">歬＝前【史】</note><note n="0255011" resp="ihp" type="mod">歬【佛拓】，前【史】</note><app n="0255011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】">歬</rdg></app>。靈河
<lb ed="I" n="0255b22" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">其</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">後</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">望</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">景</unclear>□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">興</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">賢</unclear>□勝地真粵福田。於是苦行異人。慧心高德。皆通九<note n="0255012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">郶＝部【史】</note><note n="0255012" resp="ihp" type="mod">郶【佛拓】，部【史】</note><app n="0255012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">部</lem><rdg wit="【原】">郶</rdg></app>。咸曉二禪。乃振
<lb ed="I" n="0255b23" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">錫</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">來</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">儀</unclear>。□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">風</unclear>□□□□□□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">成</unclear>田。高山<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">虧</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">而</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">作</unclear>□。故豐碑宜勒。銅柱須標。徽猷盛事。無殞長葉。其詞云。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b24" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">覺</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">理</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">常</unclear>□。□□□□。□□□□。□□□□。□□□□。□□同<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歸</unclear>。大師□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遠</unclear>。空<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">播</unclear>音<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">徽</unclear>。<note place="inline"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">其</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">一</unclear></note>彼岸須登。寶舟宜運。劫石期盡。肌膚何悋。聖帝英王。
<lb ed="I" n="0255b25" type="honorific"/>□□□□。□□□□。□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">能</unclear>□。<note place="inline"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">其</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">二</unclear></note>□□□□。□□□□□□□□。是屬貞明。瓊宮□氣。瑤室和精。氛氳降祉。生此人英。<note place="inline">其三</note>慧劍既佩。誡珠是
<lb ed="I" n="0255b26" type="honorific"/>□。□□□□。□□□□。□□□□。□□□□。□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">興</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">干</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">臨</unclear>旭。<note place="inline"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">其</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">四</unclear></note><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雕</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梁</unclear>□柱。□壁丹櫨。朱扉玉砌。青瑣金鋪。風鳴韻鐸。日照和珠。高山仰
<lb ed="I" n="0255b27" type="honorific"/>□。□□□□。□□□□□□。□□□□。□□□□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">城</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">隩</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">潤</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">招</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">提</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>構。□□□□。三乘七覺。衢<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">道</unclear>俟問。<note place="inline">其六</note>山虧一匱。海涸三田。殷墟闃寂。周室
